/ut7 is a french cooperative self-managed by its employees, an IT consulting company and an approved training organization. Since 2008, it has been hosting a collective of experienced programmers who boast of the agile methods of software development movement, and who have a very solid expertise on the subject.

We use all means at our disposal to convey our understanding of agility and software development professions. Our ambition is to give professional developers the means and motivation to (re)value their business, to raise the level of expectations a client may have of themselves, to raise the level of expectations they may have of themselves.

